c: 24
v: 41
t: "Hauoni here (Muhammad (SAW)) kuti Allah vanokudzwa newese ari mudenga uye ari panyika, uye neshiri dzakavhura mapapiro adzo (dzichibhururuka)? Chimwe nechimwe chacho (Allah) zvirokwazvo vanoziva manamatiro acho uye marumbidziro acho (Allah), uye Allah vanoziva zvikuru zvose zvavanoita"